<item>
            <title>[KAFKA-9056] Selector outbound byte metric does not count partial sends</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-9056</link>
                <project id="12311720" key="KAFKA">Kafka</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently the outbound byte metric is updated only after a `Send` is complete. If the client disconnects before completion, then the metric is not updated even if some of the data had been sent.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="13262740">KAFKA-9056</key>
